    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely dice the <strong>onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Tear the <strong>meat-free chicken </strong>into smaller strips</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
